   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="uoedh_hl_h.710_1.jpg"/>

            <note rend="pencil" hand="other">16</note>

            <opener>


               <address rend="letterhead">
                  <addrLine>Max Gate,</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Dorchester</addrLine>
               </address>
               <dateline>
                  <date when="1910-09-27"> Sept 27: 1910</date>
               </dateline>

               <salute>Dear Captain Acland:</salute>

            </opener>

            <p>At last I have the pleasure of acceding to the request of the Council &amp; yourself,
               &amp; send a complete set of my writings in prose &amp; verse up to date â€“ so far as
               they have been collected. A few are not yet printed in volume form, but those I hope
               you may receive hereafter.</p>



            <closer>

               <salute>Believe me</salute>
               <salute>Yours very truly</salute>
               <signed>Thomas Hardy.</signed>

            </closer>


            <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.710_2.jpg"/>

         </div>
      </body>
